      "description": "CFD-predicted hemolysis index values compared against in-vitro measurements from the FDA generic centrifugal pump test rig across 5 operating points. Normalised index error within 18% at 4 of 5 operating points.",
      "prov:wasGeneratedBy": "https://uofa.net/synth/activity/hemolysis-validation-run-2024",
